  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Colorable
    Colorable interface.
    FillColorable  
    GraphicsObserver
    Observer pattern interface used to notify a canvas to repaint if a graphical object has changed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Arc
    Used to draw an arc on the CanvasWindow or GraphicsGroup.
    CanvasWindow
    Creates a window frame and canvas panel that is used to draw graphical objects.
    Ellipse
    Used to draw an ellipse on the screen.
    GraphicsGroup
    This is a graphical object that is used to group other graphical objects together.
    GraphicsObject
    Abstract class representing some sort of graphical object that can be drawn and positioned in a canvaswindow.
    GraphicsText
    Represents a string of text that is drawn in a canvas window Created by bjackson on 10/10/2016.
    Image
    Used to draw an image on the screen.
    Line
    Represents a line that can be drawn graphically in a canvaswindow Created by bjackson on 9/14/2016.
    Rectangle
    Represents a 2D rectangle that is drawn on the screen.
